  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "咱们来梳理一下零售系统的核心流程吧。我想从优惠券系统开始，它应该是整个订单流的触发点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，优惠券系统作为入口。那它下游直接对接订单管理吗？还是中间有其他环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "直接对接订单管理，但订单管理内部其实有三个连续的处理阶段，我需要把它们拆成B、C、D三个节点来体现状态流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，B到C再到D，三个顺序节点。那D之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "D之后要进入一个循环处理，我们业务上叫\"每笔提交迁移\"，里面涉及库存扣减和订单状态回写。这个得用子图框起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "子图内部是D→E→F→G？E和G都是订单管理，F是库存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，E处理预占，F实际扣库存，G确认回写。循环结束后到客户忠诚度系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，子图包裹D到G的循环。G出来连到H，也就是客户忠诚度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "H",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，忠诚度算完积分后，还要最终确认库存释放吗？还是直接结束？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按常规流程，积分计算完应该回到库存做最终确认，我加个J节点表示库存的终态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H",
        "J",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，J作为库存的最终确认节点。不过循环里的F和最后的J都是库存，要区分清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "F",
        "J",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，F是循环内的库存扣减，J是流程终点的库存确认。整体结构应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "F",
        "J",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我刚发现B到C的箭头画错了，应该是B指向C，不是C指向B。顺序不能反。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修正了，B→C→D的顺序流转。还有其他问题吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "子图的标题\"LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE\"能显示全吗？业务方特别在意这个命名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "显示完整，子图标题就是这个。那A到B的箭头需要标注什么说明吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "暂时不用标注，保持简洁。但我确认一下节点命名：A是优惠券系统，B、C、D、E、G都是订单管理的不同阶段，F和J是库存，H是忠诚度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "H",
        "J",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "核对无误。G到H是循环出口到忠诚度，H到J是最终库存确认。整个流程闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "H",
        "J",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "J之后真的结束了吗？不需要再回到订单管理做归档？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "J",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "当前代码里J是终点。如果需要归档，我可以再加一个K节点连回订单管理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "J",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "先保持这样，J作为终点。归档是另一个批处理流程，不放在这个实时流里。就这样定稿吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
